<div class="campaigns-container">
  <div class="campaigns-header">
    <h2>🎯 Earn 活动配置（Nacos）</h2>
    <p>
      可视化编辑 Nacos 配置：<code>xhunt_campaigns</code>（结构：<code>{ version, campaigns: [] }</code>）
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="campaigns-toolbar">
    <div class="left">
      <span class="muted"
        >当前 dataId：<code id="campaigns-dataid">xhunt_campaigns</code></span
      >
      <span class="muted">group：<code>DEFAULT_GROUP</code></span>
    </div>

    <div class="right">
      <div class="campaigns-search">
        <span class="icon">🔍</span>
        <input
          id="campaigns-search"
          type="text"
          placeholder="搜索活动（id / campaignKey / 标题）"
        />
      </div>
      <button class="btn primary" id="campaigns-refresh">🔄 从 Nacos 重新加载</button>
      <button class="btn" id="campaigns-new">➕ 新增活动</button>
      <button class="btn" id="campaigns-duplicate" disabled>🧬 复制活动</button>
      <button class="btn danger" id="campaigns-delete" disabled>🗑️ 删除当前</button>
      <button class="btn success" id="campaigns-publish" disabled>
        🚀 发布到 Nacos
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaigns-body">
    <div class="list">
      <div class="list-header">
        <strong>活动列表</strong>
        <span class="muted" id="campaigns-count">0 个</span>
      </div>
      <div class="list-items" id="campaigns-list"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="editor">
      <div class="editor-header">
        <div>
          <strong>编辑</strong>
          <span class="muted" id="campaigns-editor-hint">选择左侧一条活动开始编辑</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="campaigns-editor-empty" class="editor-empty">
        <div class="empty-title">请选择左侧一条活动</div>
        <div class="empty-desc">
          从左侧列表点击任一活动即可开始编辑；你也可以点击上方
          <strong>「新增活动」</strong> 来创建新的 Earn 活动。
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="campaigns-editor-body" style="display: none">
        <div class="field-row field-row-toggle">
          <div class="field">
            <label>活动启用（enabled）</label>
            <label class="switch">
              <input id="campaigns-enabled" type="checkbox" disabled />
              <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label>测试期（testingPhase）</label>
            <label class="switch">
              <input id="campaigns-testingPhase" type="checkbox" disabled />
              <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row field-row-2">
          <div class="field">
            <label>投放活动者的推特号</label>
            <input id="campaigns-twitter-handle" type="text" placeholder="例如：bybit" />
            <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
              填写后会自动填充 id、campaignKey、hotTweetsKey。保存后不可修改。
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
              <span>是否有早期项目提示</span>
              <span class="risk-preview-trigger" title="悬停查看预览">ℹ️</span>
            </label>
            <label class="switch">
              <input id="campaigns-hasRiskConfirm" type="checkbox" disabled />
              <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
            <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
              勾选后会在活动页面显示早期项目风险提示
            </div>
            <div class="risk-preview-popup" id="risk-preview-popup" style="display: none;">
              <div class="risk-preview-content">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px;">中文预览：</div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">
                  <strong>重要提示：</strong>该项目为 Early-stage 项目，信息由项目方提供，请在参与前自行判断。点击继续即表示理解并接受。
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px;">English Preview:</div>
                <div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">
                  <strong>Important Notice:</strong> The project is in its early stage. The information is provided by the project team. Please make an informed decision before participating. Proceeding indicates that you understand and accept this.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-collapsible">
          <div class="section-title section-title-collapsible">
            <span>高级配置（id / campaignKey / hotTweetsKey）</span>
            <span class="section-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="section-content" style="display: none;">
            <div class="field-row">
              <div class="field">
                <label>id（唯一）</label>
                <input id="campaigns-id" type="text" placeholder="例如：bybit-hunter" disabled />
                <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
                  内部索引使用，无需手动维护（自动生成：campaignKey + '-hunter'）
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>campaignKey</label>
                <input id="campaigns-campaignKey" type="text" placeholder="例如：bybit" disabled />
                <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
                  需要后端协商一致，一般也是投放者推特号，用于存储报名数据和排名数据
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>hotTweetsKey</label>
                <input
                  id="campaigns-hotTweetsKey"
                  type="text"
                  placeholder="例如：bybit"
                  disabled
                />
                <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
                  建议填写投放者的推特号，目的是获取热门推文数据 <code>hot?project=hotTweetsKey</code>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">活动全称（DisplayName）</div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>中文</label>
              <input id="campaigns-displayName-zh" type="text" />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>English</label>
              <input id="campaigns-displayName-en" type="text" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>活动短标题（zh）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-copy-shortTitle-zh" type="text" />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>shortTitle（en）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-copy-shortTitle-en" type="text" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-block">
            <div class="section-title-inline">项目介绍</div>
            <div class="field-row">
              <div class="field" style="flex: 1;">
                <label>项目介绍（纯文本）</label>
                <textarea
                  id="campaigns-projectIntroduction"
                  rows="3"
                  placeholder="一段纯文本介绍本项目/活动..."
                ></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-block">
            <div class="section-title-inline">
              ✍️ 写作相关主题
              <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-writing-themes-add" type="button" disabled>
                ➕ 添加主题
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="repeaters-hint">← 左右滑动 · 至少保留一个主题</div>
            <div class="repeaters-horizontal" id="campaigns-writing-themes"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">活动时间范围（Enrollment Window）</div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>startAt（活动开始时间）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-startAt" type="datetime-local" />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>endAt（活动结束时间）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-endAt" type="datetime-local" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">奖励配置</div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-3">
            <div class="field">
              <label>奖励金额 (这里写：除开征文大赛的奖励金额，总金额-征文大赛金额)</label>
              <input
                id="campaigns-rewardAmount"
                type="number"
                min="1"
                max="99999999"
                placeholder="1-99999999"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>人数</label>
              <input
                id="campaigns-rewardParticipantCount"
                type="number"
                min="10"
                max="1000"
                placeholder="10-1000"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>分配机制</label>
              <select id="campaigns-rewardDistributionType">
                <option value="">请选择</option>
                <option value="equal">平分</option>
                <option value="mindshare">mindshare分</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>奖励金额展示单位</label>
              <input
                id="campaigns-rewardUnit"
                type="text"
                placeholder="例如：U、USDT、USD"
              />
              <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
                适用于所有奖励的展示单位
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                <span>是否开启征文大赛</span>
              </label>
              <label class="switch">
                <input id="campaigns-enableEssayContest" type="checkbox" disabled />
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="essay-contest-fields" style="display: none;">
            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>征文大赛金额</label>
                <input
                  id="campaigns-essayContestAmount"
                  type="number"
                  min="0"
                  placeholder="0"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>获奖人数</label>
                <input
                  id="campaigns-essayContestWinnerCount"
                  type="number"
                  min="1"
                  placeholder="例如：10"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 8px;">
              🏆 征文大赛最终名单
              <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-essay-winners-add" type="button" disabled>
                ➕ 添加获奖者
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="repeaters-hint">← 左右滑动</div>
            <div class="repeaters" id="campaigns-essay-winners"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">门槛</div>
          <div class="field-row">
            <div class="field">
              <label>门槛</label>
              <select id="campaigns-threshold">
                <option value="">请选择</option>
                <option value="50k">50k</option>
                <option value="100k">100k</option>
                <option value="200k">200k</option>
                <option value="200k+creator">200k+creator</option>
              </select>
              <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
                硬性条件（不可修改）：报名者必须满足注册时间早于1个月并且分数数量不少于50个
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-collapsible">
          <div class="section-title section-title-collapsible">
            <span>报名按钮文案（通常不改）</span>
            <span class="section-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="section-content" style="display: none;">
            <div class="field-row field-row-3">
              <div class="field">
                <label>emoji</label>
                <input id="campaigns-copy-emoji" type="text" placeholder="例如：🎉" />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>ctaText（zh）</label>
                <input id="campaigns-copy-ctaText-zh" type="text" />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>ctaText（en）</label>
                <input id="campaigns-copy-ctaText-en" type="text" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>去官方按钮文案（zh）</label>
                <input id="campaigns-copy-goToOfficialText-zh" type="text" />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>goToOfficialText（en）</label>
                <input id="campaigns-copy-goToOfficialText-en" type="text" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>查看官方指南按钮文案（zh）</label>
                <input id="campaigns-copy-viewGuideText-zh" type="text" />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>viewGuideText（en）</label>
                <input id="campaigns-copy-viewGuideText-en" type="text" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">相关链接（Links）</div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>官方指南链接( 可以是推特介绍活动链接，也可以是其他)</label>
              <input
                id="campaigns-links-guideUrl"
                type="text"
                placeholder="https://..."
              />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>活动页面（可以是官网活动链接，也可以是推特介绍活动链接）</label>
              <input
                id="campaigns-links-activeUrl"
                type="text"
                placeholder="https://..."
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row">
            <div class="field">
              <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                <span>是否出现「查看官方排行榜」</span>
              </label>
              <label class="switch">
                <input id="campaigns-links-showLeaderboardLink" type="checkbox" disabled />
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
              <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4">
                勾选后活动页会展示查看官方排行榜入口
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">相关名单（每行一个）</div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>内部测试人员名单</label>
              <textarea
                id="campaigns-testList"
                rows="3"
                placeholder="luoyukun4"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>📍在哪些推特号右侧展示本活动</label>
              <textarea
                id="campaigns-targetUserIds"
                rows="3"
                placeholder="bybit_web3&#10;Bybit__Alpha"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">
            Ⓜ️活动方 logo
            <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-logos-add" type="button" disabled>
              ➕ 添加 Logo
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="repeaters-hint">← 左右滑动</div>
          <div class="repeaters" id="campaigns-logos"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">
            🎯报名前需完成的任务（Tasks）
            <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-tasks-add" type="button" disabled>
              ➕ 添加任务
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="repeaters-hint">← 左右滑动</div>
          <div class="repeaters" id="campaigns-tasks"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaigns-toast" id="campaigns-toast" style="display: none"></div>

  <!-- JSON 预览模态框（发布前预览） -->
  <div class="json-preview-modal-overlay" id="campaigns-json-preview-modal" style="display: none">
    <div class="json-preview-modal-panel">
      <div class="json-preview-modal-header">
        <h3>预览 JSON 配置</h3>
        <button class="close-btn" id="campaigns-json-preview-modal-close" type="button">
          &times;
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="json-preview-modal-body">
        <div class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 8px">
          即将发布到 Nacos 的完整配置（dataId: <code id="campaigns-json-preview-dataid">xhunt_campaigns</code>）
          <span id="campaigns-json-preview-diff-hint" style="margin-left: 12px; color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 600;"></span>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
          <span style="background: #fee2e2; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;">红色</span>表示删除的内容
          <span style="background: #dcfce7; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;">绿色</span>表示新增的内容
        </div>
        <div class="json-diff-container">
          <div class="json-diff-side">
            <div class="json-diff-header">原始配置</div>
            <pre id="campaigns-json-preview-original"></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="json-diff-side">
            <div class="json-diff-header">修改后配置</div>
            <pre id="campaigns-json-preview-content"></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="json-preview-modal-footer">
        <button class="btn" id="campaigns-json-preview-modal-cancel" type="button">
          取消
        </button>
        <button class="btn primary" id="campaigns-json-preview-modal-confirm" type="button">
          确认发布
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- JSON 源码编辑模态框 -->
  <div class="json-modal-overlay" id="campaigns-json-modal" style="display: none">
    <div class="json-modal-panel">
      <div class="json-modal-header">
        <h3 id="campaigns-json-modal-title">编辑 JSON</h3>
        <button class="close-btn" id="campaigns-json-modal-close" type="button">
          &times;
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="json-modal-body">
        <textarea
          id="campaigns-json-source"
          placeholder="请输入或粘贴 JSON..."
          spellcheck="false"
        ></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="json-modal-footer">
        <button class="btn" id="campaigns-json-modal-cancel" type="button">
          取消
        </button>
        <button class="btn primary" id="campaigns-json-modal-save" type="button">
          保存
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .campaigns-container {
    padding: 14px;
    max-width: 1600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .campaigns-header h2 {
    margin: 0 0 3px;
    color: #111827;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .campaigns-header p {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .campaigns-toolbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  .campaigns-toolbar .left {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .campaigns-toolbar .right {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .btn.btn-sm {
    padding: 5px 9px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .campaigns-search {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    min-width: 240px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .campaigns-search .icon {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }
  .campaigns-search input {
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 2px 0;
    background: transparent;
  }
  .campaigns-search input::placeholder {
    color: #9ca3af;
  }
  .campaigns-search:focus-within {
    border-color: #3b82f6;
    background: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
  }
  .muted {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .campaigns-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 360px 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .campaigns-body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .list {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  .list-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: #fafafa;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .list-items {
    max-height: calc(100vh - 280px);
    overflow: auto;
  }
  .item {
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.15s;
  }
  .item:hover {
    background: #f9fafb;
  }
  .item.active {
    background: #eff6ff;
    border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6;
  }
  .chips {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 4px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .chip {
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    color: #374151;
    background: #fff;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .chip.on {
    border-color: #86efac;
    background: #ecfdf5;
    color: #065f46;
  }
  .chip.testing {
    border-color: #fde68a;
    background: #fffbeb;
    color: #92400e;
  }
  .item-meta {
    font-size: 11px;
